race.description: Life Member Mr Cam Sorell Maiden Plate
race.comment: Tough race with a myriad of these close to getting off the mark. CARNOTAURUS (8) could be value here. Narrow fourth two back then runner-up latest over a mile. Will be strong to the line over the 1400m here and very well weighted with the claim. Looks a top chance. FIERCE 'N FABULOUS (13) is fitter for two runs back and has hit the line hard at both. Overdue and will take beating. DON TURBOAS (6) is a three start maiden and has placed all three. Senior rider aboard to handle the tricky gate and looks a top chance on best figures. LORD HEAR US (2) resumed form a long break over 1400m and turned in an eye-catching run. Placed 2/3 course and distance and is yet another close to breaking through.
